373
00:21:17,442 --> 00:21:18,777
Q-17.

374
00:21:24,574 --> 00:21:25,492
Harris.

375
00:21:25,742 --> 00:21:26,827
Q-17.

376
00:21:28,203 --> 00:21:29,454
